---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL || '/';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Hiring GitHub Readme"
  description="Privacy policy for Hiring GitHub Readme, including analytics and cookie consent details."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen px-4 py-10">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-xl border border-gh-border/70 bg-gh-card/45 p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-5">
      <header class="space-y-2">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gh-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary text-sm">Last updated: March 19, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
        This website is a personal project operated by Vitalii Popov. I respect your privacy and collect only
        the minimum data needed to understand product usage and improve the app.
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gh-text">What Data Is Processed</h2>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
          When analytics consent is granted, Google Analytics 4 may process technical usage data such as page views,
          approximate location (region/city), device/browser information, and anonymized interaction metrics.
          I do not intentionally send personal identifiers such as names, emails, or private content to analytics.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gh-text">Purpose and Legal Basis</h2>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
          Analytics is used only to understand usage trends and improve this product. For visitors in the EU/EEA,
          analytics cookies are enabled only after explicit consent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gh-text">Cookies and Consent</h2>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
          By default, analytics storage is disabled. You can accept or decline analytics in the cookie banner.
          You can also change your decision anytime using the "Manage Cookies" button in the footer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gh-text">Third-Party Processors</h2>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
          This site uses Google Analytics (Google Ireland Limited / Google LLC) and Vercel hosting.
          Data processing by third parties is subject to their own privacy terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gh-text">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
          Retention settings are managed in the Google Analytics property. Data is retained only as long as
          needed for aggregated analytics reporting.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gh-text">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gh-text-secondary">
          For privacy questions, contact: <a class="text-gh-accent underline underline-offset-2" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mskvitalii/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vitalii Popov</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer class="pt-2">
        <a
          href={`${base}`}
          class="inline-flex px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-gh-accent text-gh-bg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          Back to Scanner
        </a>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
